#: .\monster_attacks.json
msgid "napalm spit"
msgid_plural "napalm spits"
msgstr[0] "凝固汽油吐息"

#: .\monster_attacks.json
msgid "Fake gun that fires napalm globs."
msgstr "发射凝固汽油团的假枪。"

#: .\monster_attacks.json
msgid "auto"
msgstr "自动"

#: .\monster_attacks.json
msgctxt "gun_type_type"
msgid "rifle"
msgstr "步枪"

#: .\monster_attacks.json
msgid "napalm bomb"
msgid_plural "napalm bombs"
msgstr[0] "凝固汽油炸弹"

#: .\monster_attacks.json
msgid "Fake gun that fires napalm."
msgstr "发射凝固汽油的假枪。"

#: .\monsters.json
msgid "giant fire ant"
msgid_plural "giant fire ants"
msgstr[0] "巨型火蚁"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'giant fire ant'}
#: .\monsters.json
msgid ""
"A monstrous firey-orange ant with a slighty, glowing abdomen, that ends with"
" a small stinger at the tip."
msgstr "一只巨大的火橙色蚂蚁，腹部微微发光，末端带有一根小刺针。"

#: .\monsters.json
msgid "Fire ant manibles click with a spark, launching firey spit!"
msgstr "火蚁的颚咔哒作响，迸出火花，喷射出炽热的唾液！"

#: .\monsters.json
msgid "fire ant larva"
msgid_plural "fire ant larvas"
msgstr[0] "火蚁幼虫"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'fire ant larva'}
#: .\monsters.json
msgid ""
"A squirming light-yellow grub that seems to be drippling a tanish jellified-"
"liquid from both ends of its body."
msgstr "一条蠕动的浅黄色蛆虫，身体两端似乎都在滴落着棕黄色的胶状液体。"

#: .\monsters.json
msgid "fire queen ant"
msgid_plural "fire queen ants"
msgstr[0] "火蚁蚁后"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'fire queen ant'}
#: .\monsters.json
msgid ""
"An enormous firey-orange ant with an elongated, pulsating abdomen.  Its "
"orifice seems developed only for egg-laying rather than spraying flammable "
"napalm like the rest of the colony, but it doesn't seem affected by fire "
"either."
msgstr "一只巨大的火橙色蚂蚁，腹部细长且脉动着。它的孔口似乎仅用于产卵，而非像蚁群其他成员那样喷射易燃的凝固汽油，但它似乎也不受火焰影响。"

#: .\monsters.json
msgid "fire soldier ant"
msgid_plural "fire soldier ants"
msgstr[0] "火蚁兵蚁"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'fire soldier ant'}
#: .\monsters.json
msgid ""
"A massive firey-orange ant that towers over the worker ants with a giant "
"head crest.  Along with its huge mandibles, a highly violatie ooze seeps "
"from the end of its bloated abdomen."
msgstr "一只巨大的火橙色蚂蚁，头冠庞大，高耸于工蚁之上。除了巨大的颚部，其肿胀的腹部末端还渗出一种高度易爆的黏液。"

#: .\monsters.json
msgid "Fire ant manibles click with a spark, launching a glob of firey spit!"
msgstr "火蚁的颚咔哒作响，迸出火花，喷射出一团炽热的唾液！"

#: .\monsters.json
msgid "ember bloated zombie"
msgid_plural "ember bloated zombies"
msgstr[0] "余烬肿胀僵尸"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'ember bloated zombie'}
#: .\monsters.json
msgid ""
"With its ember skin swollen to near rupture with methane gas, this cyst "
"covered zombie looks like it could violently burst under the slightest of "
"disturbances, and fire would probably be a very bad idea."
msgstr "其余烬皮肤因甲烷气体肿胀至近乎破裂，这只布满囊肿的僵尸看起来在轻微扰动下就可能猛烈爆炸，而火焰很可能是个非常糟糕的主意。"

#: .\monsters.json
msgid "volatile zombie"
msgid_plural "volatile zombies"
msgstr[0] "易爆僵尸"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'volatile zombie'}
#: .\monsters.json
msgid ""
"A sickly-looking dead one.  Its skin looks especially thin, with a peculiar,"
" colorless fluid flowing through the clearly visible veins."
msgstr "一只病态的死者。它的皮肤看起来特别薄，一种奇特的无色液体在清晰可见的血管中流动。"

#: .\monsters.json
msgid "Volatile zombie ejects firey spit!"
msgstr "易爆僵尸喷射出炽热的唾液！"

#: .\monsters.json
msgid "fire spitter zombie"
msgid_plural "fire spitter zombies"
msgstr[0] "喷火僵尸"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'fire spitter zombie'}
#: .\monsters.json
msgid ""
"A hunched human body with its eyes pushed up into its forehead and drooping "
"cheeks, most of its face is occupied by a puckered mouth.  Its stomach is "
"swollen and nearly translucent, with a sickly colorless tint."
msgstr "一个佝偻的人体，眼睛上翻至额头，脸颊下垂，大部分面部被一张撅起的嘴占据。它的腹部肿胀且近乎透明，带着病态的苍白色调。"

#: .\monsters.json
msgid "Spitter vomits out a glob of firey spit!"
msgstr "喷吐者呕出一团炽热的唾液！"

#: .\monsters.json
msgid "incendiary zombie"
msgid_plural "incendiary zombies"
msgstr[0] "燃烧僵尸"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'incendiary zombie'}
#: .\monsters.json
msgid ""
"This body has swollen to immense proportions, but still manages to hold "
"itself together with semi-congealed colorless liquid all over its bloated "
"body.  It clumsily moves around, but somehow attacks with a large reserve of"
" highly flammable liquid."
msgstr "这具躯体已肿胀到巨大无比，但依然通过遍布浮肿身体的半凝固无色液体勉强维持着形态。它笨拙地移动着，却不知为何能利用大量高度易燃液体进行攻击。"

#: .\monsters.json
msgid "Incendiary zombie spits a wad of fire!"
msgstr "燃烧僵尸吐出一团火焰！"

#: .\monsters.json
msgid "Incendiary zombie vomits up a glob of flamming spit!"
msgstr "燃烧僵尸呕出一团燃烧的唾液！"

#: .\monsters.json
msgid "crimson zombie"
msgid_plural "crimson zombies"
msgstr[0] "深红僵尸"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'crimson zombie'}
#: .\monsters.json
msgid ""
"A human body with crimson flesh, occasionally a flicker of flame can be "
"seen."
msgstr "一具深红色血肉的人体，偶尔可见火焰闪烁。"

#: .\monsters.json
msgid "crimson brute"
msgid_plural "crimson brutes"
msgstr[0] "深红蛮兽"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'crimson brute'}
#: .\monsters.json
msgid ""
"A huge, crimson beast covered in visible scarring from what you can only "
"guess was 'research'.  Being near it, you can feel intense heat emanating "
"from it."
msgstr "一头巨大的深红野兽，全身布满可见的疤痕，你只能猜测那是“研究”所致。靠近它时，你能感受到它散发出的强烈热量。"

#: .\monsters.json
msgid "inferno husk"
msgid_plural "inferno husks"
msgstr[0] "地狱空壳"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'inferno husk'}
#: .\monsters.json
msgid ""
"This once-human is visible only as a glowing crimson silhouette that you "
"have to squint to see, cloaked in a  field of flames that flicker intensely."
" It walks slowly and deliberately, the raging inferno around it dances "
"wildly."
msgstr ""
"这个曾经的人类现在只是一个发光的深红轮廓，你必须眯眼才能看清，它被一层剧烈闪烁的火焰场笼罩。它缓慢而谨慎地行走，周围狂暴的地狱之火疯狂舞动。"

#: .\monsters.json
msgid "exterminator bot"
msgid_plural "exterminator bots"
msgstr[0] "灭杀机器人"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'exterminator bot'}
#: .\monsters.json
msgid ""
"The Northrop Exterminator F-4 was a production series of flamethrower "
"exterminator robots. Commissioned & designed for use of controlled burns, "
"and extreme pest control, it rolls on a set of hydraulic treads and is armed"
" with an intimidating flamethrower."
msgstr ""
"诺斯罗普灭杀者F-4是火焰喷射灭杀机器人的量产系列。受委托设计用于控制性焚烧和极端害虫防治，它依靠一套液压履带移动，并配备了一具令人生畏的火焰喷射器。"

#: .\monsters.json
msgid "exterminator tank"
msgid_plural "exterminator tanks"
msgstr[0] "灭杀坦克"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'exterminator tank'}
#: .\monsters.json
msgid ""
"The Northrop Exterminator FT-X was a prototype series of flamethrower "
"exterminator tanks. Clearly engineered by a someone who found a nest of "
"unspeakable critters that drove that person to convert the F-4's into "
"overkill Flamethrower tanks also armed with vulcan napalm bomb launchers."
msgstr ""
